data.title: New Student Enrollment
data.meta_description: Centerville City Schools provides this information to help families enroll new students in the district.
data.text:
Online registration for the UPCOMING 2024-25 school year is now open! Students must be enrolled by Monday, Aug. 5, 2024 to ensure they can begin on the first day of school on Aug. 14.

Preschool: Enrollment for Centerville Preschool is conducted separately from K-12 enrollment. Please click here for information about Preschool Enrollment.
